Detailed Description

cvmx_gmx::_tx_hg2_reg1

Notes: The TX_XOF[15:0] field in GMX(0)_TX_HG2_REG1 and the TX_XON[15:0] field in GMX(0)_TX_HG2_REG2 register map to the same 16 physical flops. When written with address of GMX(0)_TX_HG2_REG1, it will exhibit write 1 to set behavior and when written with address of GMX(0)_TX_HG2_REG2, it will exhibit write 1 to clear behavior. For reads, either address will return the $GMX(0)_TX_HG2_REG1 values.
